================================================================================
CALCULATED GAUGE SERIES
================================================================================

The numerical output of calculated / virtual gauges — gauges whose values are
computed from a formula stored in calc_expression — is also licensed under
CC BY-NC 4.0. Although the inputs are public-domain observations, the
formulas themselves are curatorial work; the resulting series exists only
because of the curator's expression.

================================================================================
OBSERVATION TIME-SERIES
================================================================================

The raw observation values stored in the observation table — the numbers
fetched from government agencies — are in the public domain at source.

U.S. federal agency data is not subject to copyright under 17 U.S.C. § 105.
State agency data is generally public records (state-specific terms apply
but are similarly permissive).

Data sources (please credit the originating agency when redistributing):

    - U.S. Geological Survey (USGS)
      https://waterdata.usgs.gov/
    - National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration (NOAA),
      via the Northwest River Forecast Center
      https://www.nwrfc.noaa.gov/
    - U.S. Army Corps of Engineers (USACE)
    - U.S. Bureau of Reclamation (USBR)
      https://www.usbr.gov/pn/hydromet/
    - Idaho Department of Water Resources (IDWR)
    - Washington State Department of Ecology
    - Oregon Department of Environmental Quality

Anyone is free to fetch observation data directly from the originating source.

